<h2 style="color: #1A1A1A; margin-top: 0;">Thank You for Reaching Out!</h2>

<p>Dear {{customerName}},</p>

<p>We have received your message and will get back to you as soon as possible. Our team typically responds within 24 hours during business days.</p>

<div class="info-box">
  <p><span class="label">Subject:</span> {{subject}}</p>
  <p><span class="label">Your Message:</span></p>
  <p style="margin-top: 4px; white-space: pre-wrap;">{{message}}</p>
</div>

<p>If your matter is urgent, you can also reach us via WhatsApp or by calling us directly.</p>

<p style="text-align: center;">
  <a href="{{storeUrl}}/pages/contact" class="btn-primary">Contact Us Again</a>
</p>

<p>
  Best regards,<br />
  <strong style="color: #D4AF37;">{{businessName}} Team</strong>
</p>
